 chutney on the side.\n<h3>Video</h3>\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aJdU-Y_4cig', 'Spicy Herb Chicken Pasta', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'spicy-herb-chicken-pasta-2', '', '', '2017-01-03 09:11:08', '2017-01-03 09:11:08', '', 0, 'http://td_uid_25_586b6aac0b51c', 0, 'post', '', 0),
